---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
---

<Layout title="Projects | Ernests Smalikis">
	<Navbar />
	<main class="content-container pt-32 pb-20">
		<section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-16">
			<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-10 gradient-text text-center drop-shadow-lg animate-fade-in">üìê What I Build</h1>
			<div class="glass-card p-10 md:p-14 mb-12 animate-slide-up">
				<p class="text-lg md:text-xl mb-8 text-secondary-light dark:text-secondary text-center">
					I focus on lean, high-impact software with a strong backend and security posture. My work spans:
				</p>
				<ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mb-8 text-lg">
					<li>Backend APIs & automation tools</li>
					<li>Static and full-stack web apps</li>
					<li>AI/ML-powered text processing and OSINT utilities</li>
					<li>Privacy-first tools for individuals and small businesses</li>
					<li>Real-time systems with low-latency performance requirements</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="text-lg italic mb-8 text-center text-accent">Tools are tested in the wild ‚Äî not just in dev environments.</p>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 gradient-text">Featured Projects</h2>
				<div class="space-y-8">
					<div class="glass-card p-6 border-l-4 border-primary/80">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">XStagePass</h3>
						<p>Event management software with task-based access control, Google Drive image uploads, and real-time updates. Supports both hosted and self-hosted deployments.</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="glass-card p-6 border-l-4 border-primary/80">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">LuceneX Insight</h3>
						<p>AI-driven browser tool for extracting and summarizing text while ignoring markup and noise. Designed for OSINT and journalism workflows.</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="glass-card p-6 border-l-4 border-primary/80">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">SpotEye</h3>
						<p>Surveillance optimization tool that tags and prioritizes video events using smart filtering and human-in-the-loop learning.</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="glass-card p-6 border-l-4 border-primary/80">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">XHashPass</h3>
						<p>A battle-tested evolution of my first tool ‚Äî Password generator. Lightweight, secure, and built with modern cryptographic standards in mind.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<a href="/vision" class="loud-cta mx-auto block w-max mt-8">
				<span class="inline-flex items-center gap-3">
					<span class="drop-shadow-lg text-2xl">üéØ</span>
					<span>See My Vision</span>
				</span>
			</a>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>
